<blockquote>
<p>AUSA: What did the defendant you about risk?
<br/>Ellison: He said it was OK if positive EV, expected value. He said he was willing to take large coin flips – he talked about being willing to flip a coin &amp; destroy the world, as long as a win would make it twice as good</p>
<p>— Inner City Press (@innercitypress) <a href="https://feeds.feedblitz.com/~/t/0/0/marginalrevolution/~https://twitter.com/innercitypress/status/1711821182582837296?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank" referrerpolicy="no-referrer">October 10, 2023</a></p></blockquote>
